                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-lg-6 pt-5 pb-lg-5">
                    <div class="about-text bg-white p-4 p-lg-5 my-lg-5">
                        <h6 class="text-primary text-uppercase" style="letter-spacing: 5px;">Về chúng tôi</h6>
